    "new_rules_in_this_unit": [
      "Use definite articles der (r-words), das (s-words), die (e-words) and indefinite articles ein (r-words), ein (s-words), eine (e-words) in the nominative case.",
      "Replace nouns with pronouns matching their noun class: er for r-words, es for s-words, sie for e-words.",
      "Form feminine profession nouns by adding -in to the masculine form, and use the Gendersternchen for inclusive forms."
    ],
